<AbstractNarration>DMS-990071433&lt;br/&gt;Edward Turner&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;This award provides partial support for the featured speakers and for some graduate students to attend the 2000 Albany Group Theory Conference.  The conference will be the eleventh in a series of conferences dedicated to the interplay between group theory and topology.  There will be seven main speakers, each of whom will give a one hour talk.  In addition, there will be 20 - 25 short talks by participants.  The conference will be held at the Rensselaerville Conference Center in October of 2000.  Further information is available at http://nyjm.albany.edu/~ted/00conf.html.  &lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
